data.eml:eml: New species of the genus Amphinemura (Plecoptera: Nemouridae) from Yunnan, China

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Du, Yu-Zhou, Wang, Zhi-Jie (2007): New species of the genus Amphinemura (Plecoptera: Nemouridae) from Yunnan, China. Zootaxa 1554: 57-62, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.178182
